    {
      "id": "RouxEFG_Vf6aVywZ7hOYY",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 556.1686507936506,
      "y": -662.2460317460318,
      "width": 1459.566650390625,
      "height": 141.11111111111103,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a3",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 638596856,
      "version": 89,
      "versionNonce": 268409592,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780674152729,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Design a framework that automatically generates and manages standardised, version-controlled CI/CD\n pipelines for microservices at scale. You may assume any CI/CD engine of your choice. Also explain the pipeline \nstructure itself — stages, quality gates, validations, environment promotion, and \nconfiguration management across regions. Propose strategies to minimize deployment downtime and rollback risk.",
      "fontSize": 28.222222222222204,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Design a framework that automatically generates and manages standardised, version-controlled CI/CD\n pipelines for microservices at scale. You may assume any CI/CD engine of your choice. Also explain the pipeline \nstructure itself — stages, quality gates, validations, environment promotion, and \nconfiguration management across regions. Propose strategies to minimize deployment downtime and rollback risk.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "aMOcp22UPJ_gfMUZbaJ2n",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2309.859126984127,
      "y": -388.376984126984,
      "width": 389.3333435058594,
      "height": 280,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a4",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 583058312,
      "version": 464,
      "versionNonce": 509085576,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780675661450,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Constraints\n- 500 engineers\n- 300 services\n- Builds/days: 5 000 builds/day\n- Concurrent builds: 125\n- 4 GB RAM -> 64 GB\n- Worker nodes = 50\n- 700 deployments/day",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Constraints\n- 500 engineers\n- 300 services\n- Builds/days: 5 000 builds/day\n- Concurrent builds: 125\n- 4 GB RAM -> 64 GB\n- Worker nodes = 50\n- 700 deployments/day",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "CXp5FCyxpoMJTjYIW_IBD",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 540.5734126984122,
      "y": -349.09126984126965,
      "width": 919.2000122070312,
      "height": 280,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a5",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 927235832,
      "version": 540,
      "versionNonce": 2109670648,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780672381670,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Requirements\n- Engineers want to ship their to production (building, testing, deploying)\n- Build system (test, build, push)\n    - Quality gates: testing, test coverage, linting\n    - Security gates: immutable artifact (deployable image), security scans\n- Rollout system \n   - Fetch the image and deploy\n   - Progressive (test, then promote production). Canary",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Requirements\n- Engineers want to ship their to production (building, testing, deploying)\n- Build system (test, build, push)\n    - Quality gates: testing, test coverage, linting\n    - Security gates: immutable artifact (deployable image), security scans\n- Rollout system \n   - Fetch the image and deploy\n   - Progressive (test, then promote production). Canary",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "RFz7qxfNfGnzLONot78VI",
      "type": "text",
